quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  2,261,example de those spend their monies causa DEUS est ut de grain produces 7 spikes centum grains in each spike DEUS multiplies HOC manifold PRO whomever He TESTIMENTUM. DEUS est Bounteous Knower
  2,262,Those spend their moneta causa DEUS tunc non subsequentis their charity cum insult harm receive their recompense their Dominus; they habet nihil fear nor testimentum they grieve
  2,263,Generis words compassion est bonus than charity subsequentis de insult DEUS est Rich Clement
  2,264,O vos believe non nullify tuus charities de inflicting reproach insult unus spends his moneta show dum disbelieving DEUS Extremum Feria! His example est rock covered thin layer soil heavy rain falls it lavatus est soil sinister it useless rock They gain nihil their efforts. DEUS NON guide disbelieving people
  2,265,example de those dedit their moneta seeking deus pleasure sincere conviction est ut de garden high fertile soil when heavy rain falls it dedit twice prout much crop heavy rain est available drizzle suffice. DEUS est Seer DE everything VOS PERFECIT
  2,266,any de vos wish suus garden de palm trees grapes flowing streams generous crops tunc just prout he grows veteris dum his infans est adhuc dependent eum holocaust strikes burns his garden DEUS SIC clarifies revelations VOS UT VOS reflect